# Brand Theme System

## Color Usage
- **NEVER use arbitrary color values** (e.g., `text-red-500`, `bg-blue-600`)
- **ALWAYS use semantic theme variables** from [globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css)
- **Brand Colors:**
  - Primary: `text-primary` / `bg-primary` (Teal Green #2CB1A0)
  - Secondary: `text-secondary` / `bg-secondary` (Jet Black #1C1C1C)
  - Accent: `text-accent` / `bg-accent` (Coral Orange #FF6B57)
  - Success: `text-success` / `bg-success` (Emerald Green #4CAF50)
  - Warning: `text-warning` / `bg-warning` (Amber Yellow #FFC107)
  - Error: `text-destructive` / `bg-destructive` (Tomato Red #E53935)

## Typography
- **Font System:** Noto Sans with Pretendard fallback as defined in [layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/[locale]/layout.tsx)
- **Text Colors:** Use `text-foreground`, `text-muted-foreground` for hierarchy
- **Links:** Always use `text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors`

## Component Styling
- **Cards:** Use `bg-card text-card-foreground` with `card` utility class
- **Backgrounds:** Use `bg-background` for page containers
- **Borders:** Use `border-border` instead of arbitrary border colors
- **Focus States:** Use `focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary/50`

## Brand Guidelines Compliance
- Follow [brand-theme-guidelines.md](mdc:brand-theme-guidelines.md) for all design decisions
- Maintain clean, minimal, trustworthy aesthetic
- Ensure WCAG AA contrast ratios
- Support both light and dark modes
